Note: For each blocked site, GeckoSession.NavigationDelegate.onLoadError(org.mozilla.geckoview.GeckoSession, java.lang.String, org.mozilla.geckoview.WebRequestError) with error category WebRequestError.ERROR_CATEGORY_SAFEBROWSING is called.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        The GeckoRuntimeSettings instance.
